strings.Value: "Stop this immediately! I didn't give you my permission to beat my subjects!"
"Do your job. I won't get in your way."
"Where did you meet {d|Darven}Darven{/d}?! Speak, or I'll skin you alive!"
"I don't know! I don't know anything, I swear! I've never heard that name before! Please don't beat me anymore!"
"This woman is suspected of having links with Darven. We know that he bought food from her."
"I'm telling you, I don't know who that is! I've never seen him before in my life! Please, save me from them!"
"One way or another, I'll soon find out everything I need."
